Title: The Limo
Plot: On a whim, Jerry and George take a limo from a passenger that Jerry knows never made it on the plane. While taking the limo they call Elaine & Kramer to join them for an event at Madison Square Garden, but it isn't the type of event they were hoping for.
GuestStars: Norman Brenner, Peter Krause, Suzanne Snyder, Jeremy Roberts, Jodi Baskerville, I.M. Hobson, Harley Venton, Adam Leslie, Aaron Kanarek, Ray Glanzmann
